en_221361_0	A Sri Lankan father has shot and attempted to kill his 26-year-old daughter in the Tiollo area of Padua Italy.
en_221361_1	According to Italian media reports, the 46-year-old father has tried to commit suicide after he shot and attempted to kill his 26-year-old daughter.
en_221361_2	It is reported that he tried to hang himself after his attempt to shoot himself failed.
en_221361_3	However, the Italian police intervened to save the daughter and her father.
en_221361_4	The daughter’s condition is stable but the father’s condition is critical according to the papers in Italy that has quoted from the hospital sources.
